<item>
<title>认识 Flash-KMeans：一种 IO 感知的精确 K-Means 算法，在 GPU 上比 FAISS 快 200 倍以上</title>
<link>https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/15/meet-flash-kmeans-an-io-aware-exact-k-means-that-runs-over-200x-faster-than-faiss-on-gpus/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.marktechpost.com/?p=80521</guid>
<pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 09:16:09 +0000</pubDate>
<source>marktechpost.com</source>
<description><![CDATA[【marktechpost.com】Flash-KMeans 是一种开源的、IO 感知的标准 Lloyd K-Means 实现，基于 Triton GPU 内核。它不改变数学原理或进行近似计算。FlashAssign 消除了距离矩阵的物化；Sort-Inverse Update 消除了原子竞争。在 NVIDIA H200 上，它报告端到端性能提升 17.9 倍，相比 cuML 提升 33 倍，相比 FAISS 提升超过 200 倍。本文《Meet Flash-KMeans: An IO-Aware, Exact K-Means That Runs Over 200× Faster Than FAISS on GPUs》最初发表于 MarkTechPost。<br/><br/><a href="https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/15/meet-flash-kmeans-an-io-aware-exact-k-means-that-runs-over-200x-faster-than-faiss-on-gpus/">阅读原文</a>]]></description>
</item>
